{"word":"ξηραίνω","slug":"ξηραίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ξηραίνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ξηρός'><el>ξηρός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to parch up, dry up</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to become</i> or <i>be dry, parched</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to lay dry</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>siccare</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}